{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/Attack.gif?t=1729951009\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Warmage</strong> is a <strong>roguelite grid-based turn-based tactical combat</strong> game where you play as a young warmage tasked with defending his city against an unknown evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as 12 different archetypes with unique gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Varied and refreshing tactical combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After each battle, power up your warmage and buy various attacks and items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your next mission on the city map carefully</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Differents objectives for each battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 96 spells and 55 items to combine to create the ultimate warmage</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/Battlefield1.gif?t=1729951009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a wide variety of weapons and spells to defeat waves of enemies in a turn by turn combat. Various enemies will challenge you in different ways, think carefully about each movement and each attack as a single error can put you in perilous situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/Battlefield3.gif?t=1729951009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Upgrade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the gems collected during the fights to buy new spells, upgrade the ones you already have and buy new items. With each level gained, you can upgrade one of your primary characteristics which will improve the power of your attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/Shop.png?t=1729951009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Burn them all</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now that you have a deadly warmage with powerfull spells, defeat all whom will stand in your way !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/Burn.gif?t=1729951009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Use your environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The surroundings aren't just for show, they can be your greatest ally in escaping deadly situations. Learn to harness them to your advantage !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/PushVial.gif?t=1729951009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Defend your city</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your city is attacked by an unknown evil. You have to help the citizens, others warmages and important people to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/Map.png?t=1729951009\" /></p>","achievements":{"total":0},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729951009","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/page.bg.jpg?t=1729951009","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/8de80afd3956d66c58bd23f26b658fc1f8c